column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  p.petroR5#_r, M.logmass, s.velDisp, s.subclass FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) as GN ON p.objID = GN.objID  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust as M ON s.specobjid = M.specObjID WHERE  p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class = GALAXY&&&
